em of culture, craft, and place.\",\"cta\":\"Explore\"},\"manifesto\":{\"title\":\"Our philosophy\",\"body\":\"We curate the modern African lifestyle — bridging the heritage of our land with the innovation of the future. Every detail is chosen with intention. Every experience is designed to last.\"},\"ecosystem\":{\"title\":\"One venue, three experiences\",\"subtitle\":\"Three worlds, one vision. Each reinforces the others.\",\"events\":\"The Pulse\",\"eventsDesc\":\"Cultural events that move the scene forward\",\"trading\":\"The Collection\",\"tradingDesc\":\"Automotive heritage and modern luxury\",\"realEstate\":\"The Sanctuary\",\"realEstateDesc\":\"Hospitality destinations of tomorrow\"},\"featured\":{\"events\":\"Featured Event\",\"collection\":\"The Collection\",\"sanctuary\":\"The Sanctuary\",\"viewAll\":\"View all\"},\"cta\":{\"title\":\"Let's build the future together\",\"body\":\"Groovethiopia is an invitation-centric ecosystem. We prioritize collaboration with individuals, brands, and investors who value the intersection of culture, luxury, and long-term development.\",\"button\":\"Inquire\"}},\"about\":{\"title\":\"Shaping the Future of Ethiopian Lifestyle \u0026 Culture\",\"subtitle\":\"Groove Ethiopia Trading PLC is a premier Ethiopian conglomerate dedicated to excellence across hospitality, lifestyle, and strategic trade. Rooted in Addis Ababa and deeply connected to regional and international markets, we bridge the gap between world-class service and authentic cultural experiences.\\n\\nAs a diversified powerhouse, our portfolio spans high-concept event production, premium import-export solutions, and forward-thinking real estate development. We don't just participate in the market; we define the landscape by curating the future of modern Ethiopian hospitality.\",\"partnership\":{\"title\":\"A Partnership of Visionaries.\",\"body\":\"Groovethiopia is an invitation-centric ecosystem. We prioritize collaboration with individuals, brands, and investors who value the intersection of culture, luxury, and long-term development.\",\"inquire\":\"Inquire for Partnership\",\"inquireDesc\":\"Event Production, Sound Architecture \u0026 Creative Collaboration\",\"consult\":\"Request Consultation\",\"consultDesc\":\"Luxury \u0026 Vintage Automotive Procurement\",\"invest\":\"Explore Investment\",\"investDesc\":\"Real Estate \u0026 Developmental Opportunities\"},\"manifesto\":{\"title\":\"Manifesto\",\"body\":\"We curate the modern African lifestyle. We bridge the heritage of our land with the innovation of the future. At Groovethiopia, we view real estate as the canvas for human connection, events as the architecture of culture, and trade as the procurement of excellence. We are not generalists — we are specialists in high-concept living.\"},\"mission\":{\"title\":\"Mission\",\"body\":\"To define the landscape of modern Ethiopian hospitality and culture by curating experiences, products, and destinations that exceed global standards of excellence.\"},\"vision\":{\"title\":\"Vision\",\"body\":\"A future where Ethiopia is recognized globally as a nexus of culture, craft, and considered luxury — anchored by destinations, events, and assets that move the world forward.\"},\"story\":{\"title\":\"Our story\",\"body\":\"Born in Addis Ababa from a conviction that Africa deserves world-class curation, Groovethiopia began with events that moved the local scene forward. From those first gatherings grew a portfolio spanning automotive heritage, hospitality development, and cultural production. Today, we operate as a diversified powerhouse — but our focus remains singular: curate what matters.\"},\"values\":{\"title\":\"What we value\",\"list\":[{\"title\":\"Curation\",\"body\":\"We choose deliberately. Less, but better.\"},{\"title\":\"Craft\",\"body\":\"Heritage meets precision. Every detail earns its place.\"},{\"title\":\"Cultural bridge\",\"body\":\"Rooted in Ethiopia, fluent in the world.\"},{\"title\":\"Long-term vision\",\"body\":\"We build for decades, not seasons.\"}]},\"team\":{\"title\":\"Leadership\",\"subtitle\":\"The team behind the curation\"}},\"events\":{\"title\":\"The Pulse\",\"subtitle\":\"Events \u0026 Production\",\"tagline\":\"We do not host events; we engineer cultural milestones.\",\"description\":\"Our productions are defined by the convergence of world-class electronic artistry, state-of-the-art multimedia technology, and intimate, curated environments. By integrating high-performance sound architectures and immersive visual experiences, we design atmospheres that are as profound as they are electric. Whether it is a subterranean speakeasy or a sprawling outdoor odyssey, our events cater to the discerning individual who seeks the vanguard of sensory entertainment.\",\"experience\":\"The Experience: Bespoke. Immersive. Unforgettable.\",\"shukshuta\":{\"title\":\"Shukshuta Speakeasy\",\"body\":\"Our signature intimate series — a subterranean curation of sound, atmosphere, and gathering. Each edition is a one-night world.\"},\"upcoming\":\"Upcoming\",\"past\":\"Past events\",\"services\":{\"title\":\"What we do\",\"items\":[\"Large-scale festival production\",\"Indoor \u0026 outdoor event strategy\",\"Bespoke social experiences\",\"Brand activations \u0026 launches\"]}},\"trading\":{\"title\":\"The Collection\",\"subtitle\":\"Luxury \u0026 Vintage Automotive\",\"tagline\":\"True luxury is timeless.\",\"body\":\"Our import division is dedicated exclusively to the procurement of high-value automotive assets. We curate a specialized portfolio bridging elite modern luxury vehicles with meticulously refurbished vintage classics. We do not merely import transport; we source automotive heritage, engineering excellence, and rolling works of art for the elite collector and modern connoisseur.\",\"standard\":\"The Standard: Heritage. Performance. Prestige.\",\"categories\":{\"all\":\"All\",\"modern\":\"Modern Luxury\",\"vintage\":\"Vintage Classic\"},\"specs\":\"Specifications\",\"history\":\"Provenance\",\"inquire\":\"Request Consultation\"},\"realEstate\":{\"title\":\"The Sanctuary\",\"subtitle\":\"Real Estate \u0026 Development\",\"tagline\":\"Designing the future of hospitality.\",\"vision\":\"We are evolving the landscape of leisure. Our upcoming developments are a dialogue between architectural innovation and the untamed beauty of Ethiopia. From luxury mountain retreats to forest-enveloped sanctuaries, we are crafting spaces that transcend traditional accommodation, offering a profound sense of place in an increasingly transient world.\",\"future\":\"The Future: Sustainable. Visionary. Eternal.\",\"pipeline\":\"Project pipeline\",\"philosophy\":{\"title\":\"Design philosophy\",\"body\":\"Sustainable-luxury ethos. Architectural innovation that honors the environment while providing guests with unparalleled experience.\"},\"investment\":{\"title\":\"Investment thesis\",\"body\":\"A growing middle class, rising tourism, and a global appetite for authentic African destinations create a once-in-a-generation window for visionary hospitality investment.\"},\"onDemand\":{\"title\":\"On-demand commissions\",\"body\":\"Have land? Have a vision? We build bespoke destinations to specification — from concept to operational handover.\"},\"explore\":\"Explore Investment\"},\"gallery\":{\"title\":\"Portfolio\",\"subtitle\":\"A visual journey\",\"filter\":{\"all\":\"All\",\"events\":\"Events\",\"collection\":\"Collection\",\"sanctuary\":\"Sanctuary\"}},\"partners\":{\"title\":\"Partners\",\"subtitle\":\"Trusted by the best\",\"strategic\":\"Strategic partners\",\"cultural\":\"Cultural \u0026 media partners\",\"featured\":\"Featured partner\"},\"contact\":{\"title\":\"Let's build the future together\",\"subtitle\":\"Groovethiopia Trading PLC is committed to cultivating long-term partnerships that drive innovation across the Ethiopian market.\",\"paths\":{\"events\":\"Events \u0026 Production\",\"eventsDesc\":\"Festival partnerships, activations, or Shukshuta bookings\",\"trading\":\"Trading \u0026 Import-Export\",\"tradingDesc\":\"Luxury \u0026 vintage automotive procurement\",\"realEstate\":\"Real Estate \u0026 Development\",\"realEstateDesc\":\"Investment, partnerships, project consultations\"},\"form\":{\"name\":\"Name / Organization\",\"email\":\"Email\",\"phone\":\"Phone\",\"division\":\"Nature of inquiry\",\"message\":\"Project / partnership details\",\"submit\":\"Submit Inquiry\",\"signIn\":\"Sign in with Google to submit\",\"signInRequired\":\"You'll need to sign in with Google to submit an inquiry.\"},\"details\":{\"address\":\"Headquarters\",\"email\":\"Email\",\"phone\":\"Phone\",\"hours\":\"Hours\"}},\"footer\":{\"rights\":\"All rights reserved.\",\"explore\":\"Explore\",\"connect\":\"Connect\"},\"common\":{\"viewMore\":\"View more\",\"learnMore\":\"Learn more\",\"loading\":\"Loading...\",\"submitting\":\"Submitting...\",\"error\":\"Something went wrong\",\"success\":\"Inquiry received — we'll respond within 24 hours.\"}},\"children\":[\"$L67\",\"$L68\",\"$L69\",\"$L6a\",\"$L6b\"]},\"$61\",\"$65\",1]\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"67:[\"$\",\"$L6d\",null,{},\"$29\",\"$6c\",1]\n74:D\"$75\"\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"68:[\"$\",\"main\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L15\",null,{\"parallelRouterKey\":\"children\",\"error\":\"$70\",\"errorStyles\":[\"$\",\"$L7\",null,{\"type\":\"error\",\"pagePath\":\"[locale]/error.tsx\",\"children\":[]},null,\"$71\",0],\"errorScripts\":[],\"template\":[\"$\",\"$L17\",null,{},null,\"$72\",1],\"templateStyles\":\"$undefined\",\"templateScripts\":\"$undefined\",\"notFound\":[\"$\",\"$L7\",\"c-not-found\",{\"type\":\"not-found\",\"pagePath\":\"[locale]/not-found.tsx\",\"children\":[\"$L74\",[]]},null,\"$73\",0],\"forbidden\":\"$undefined\",\"unauthorized\":\"$undefined\",\"segmentViewBoundaries\":[[\"$\",\"$L7\",null,{\"type\":\"boundary:not-found\",\"pagePath\":\"[locale]/not-found.tsx@boundary\"},null,\"$76\",1],[\"$\",\"$L7\",null,{\"type\":\"boun